$ Oracle: init parameter log_archive_dest_n
@ log_archive_dest_n

`log_archive_dest_n` (n = 1 … 32) specifies the location of the → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/redo-log-files[redo log files].

Each `log_archive_dest_n` parameter corresponds to a → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters/log_archive_dest_state_n parameter that is used to enable or disable
the redo destination.

The dynamic performance view → development/databases/Oracle/installed/dynamic-performance-views/archive_dest shows the current settings and status for each
redo transport destination.

sa:


  → development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters
